        <div class="stat"><div class="big" id="sGames">0</div><div class="lbl">games played</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Your mood this week</h3><div class="mgraph" id="mgraph"></div><p id="moodMsg" style="margin:8px 0 0"></p></div>
      <p style="color:var(--faint);font-size:.82rem">*Estimated from completed days — a rough guide, not a tracker.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="achv">
      <h1>Achievements</h1>
      <p>Unlock these as you go. <b id="achvCount">0</b>/<span id="achvTotal">0</span> earned.</p>
      <div class="achv" id="achvGrid"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="vision">
      <h1>Your why</h1>
      <p>The reset is the tool. <span class="hl">This</span> is the reason. Get honest about what you actually want — it's what pulls you through the hard days.</p>
      <div class="vision" id="visionRows" style="display:grid;gap:12px;margin:16px 0"></div>
      <p style="color:var(--faint)">Saved on this device. Re-read it any time you feel like quitting.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="games">
      <h1>Mind games</h1>
      <p>Craving a hit? Play a 1-minute game instead. Each one is <b>+15 XP</b> the first time and actually calms the urge.</p>
      <div class="tiles" id="gameTiles"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="journeys">
      <h1>Mood help</h1>
      <p>However you feel right now, there's a path through it. Tap your mood.</p>
      <div class="moodgrid" id="journeyGrid"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="quotes">
      <h1>Quotes</h1>
      <div class="qcard"><p id="qText">"…"</p><div class="by" id="qBy"></div>
        <div class="qrow"><button class="btn btn--g btn--sm" id="qSave">❤️ Save</button><button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="qNext">Next →</button><button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="qShare">📤 Share</button></div></div>
      <h3 style="margin-top:18px">Saved <span id="qSavedN" style="color:var(--faint)"></span></h3>
      <div id="qSaved"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="toolkit">
      <h1>Urge toolkit</h1>
      <p>Craving to scroll? Tap a tile, do it for 90 seconds, beat the urge — <b>+5 XP</b> each.</p>
      <div class="tiles" id="urgeTiles"></div>
      <button class="btn btn--g btn--sm" id="craveBtn">I beat a craving 💪</button>
      <span style="margin-left:10px;color:var(--faint)">Beaten: <b id="craveCount">0</b></span>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="menu">
      <h1>Dopamine menu</h1>
      <p>Bored? Tap a tile and just do it. Or roll the dice.</p>
      <button class="btn btn--g" id="rollBtn">🎲 Surprise me</button>
      <div class="tiles" id="menuTiles"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="journal">
      <h1>Journal</h1>
      <p>One honest line a day. Saves on this device automatically. <b>+10 XP.</b></p>
      <textarea id="journal" placeholder="Day 1 — didn't touch my phone for the first hour. Felt weird. Good weird."></textarea>
      <div style="margin-top:10px"><button class="btn btn--g btn--sm" id="jSave">Save</button> <span class="saved" id="jSaved">Saved ✓</span></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="help">
      <h1>The rules &amp; help</h1>
      <div class="card"><h3>The cheap-dopamine fast</h3>
        <ul class="tick"><li>No phone for the first hour after waking</li><li>No short-form video for 7 days</li><li>Notifications off except calls &amp; texts</li><li>One "boring on purpose" 10-min block daily</li></ul></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Need a hand?</h3><p style="margin:0">Reply to your order confirmation email and we'll help. You've got this. 💪</p></div>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>

<div class="dr__modal" id="drModal"><div class="dr__sheet">
  <div class="top" id="mTop"><span class="e" id="mEmoji">🔥</span><button class="x" id="mClose">✕</button></div>
  <div class="body"><div class="eyebrow" id="mTag">Day 1</div><h2 id="mTitle"></h2><div id="mBody"></div><div id="mAction"></div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="dr__toast" id="drToast"></div>
<div class="dr__cf" id="drCf"></div>

<script>
(function(){
try{
  var $=function(s,r){return (r||document).querySelector(s)},$$=function(s,r){return [].slice.call((r||document).querySelectorAll(s))};
  var KEY='dr_reset_v3',state=load();
  function load(){try{return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(KEY))||{}}catch(e){return {}}}
  function save(){try{localStorage.setItem(KEY,JSON.stringify(state))}catch(e){}}
  if(!state.done)state.done={};if(typeof state.crave!=='number')state.crave=0;if(!state.journal)state.journal='';
  if(!state.notes)state.notes={};if(!state.moods)state.moods={};if(!state.vision)state.vision={};
  if(!state.games)state.games={};if(!state.achvSeen)state.achvSeen={};if(!state.savedQ)state.savedQ=[];if(typeof state.qi!=='number')state.qi=0;

  var GRADS=['linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8a3d,#ffc24b)','linear-gradient(135deg,#ff5c8a,#7c5cff)','linear-gradient(135deg,#2bd3c6,#4f8cff)','linear-gradient(135deg,#5ad48a,#bfe65a)','linear-gradient(135deg,#ff6b6b,#ff8a3d)','linear-gradient(135deg,#7c5cff,#ff5c8a)','linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd24b,#ff8a3d)'];
  var DAYS=[
    {e:"📵",t:"Delete the worst one",a:"Delete your single most-used app for the 7 days. Turn notifications off for everything except calls & texts.",w:"That one app is your biggest dopamine leak. Removing the easiest hit forces your brain to look for slower, realer rewards — exactly the muscle we're rebuilding.",r:"Which app did you delete, and what do you usually open it to avoid feeling?"},
    {e:"🌅",t:"Phone-free first hour",a:"Don't touch your phone for the first hour after waking. Leave it across the room overnight.",w:"The first thing you feed your brain sets the baseline for the whole day. Start on a hit and everything after feels dull.",r:"How did the first hour feel without the phone? What did you do instead?"},
    {e:"🧘",t:"Boredom on purpose",a:"Sit and do nothing for 10 minutes, no phone. Let your brain feel the quiet.",w:"Boredom is withdrawal — and it's the reset working. Sitting with it teaches your brain it doesn't need constant input to be okay.",r:"What came up in the quiet? Was it as bad as you expected?"},
    {e:"🔁",t:"Swap one hit",a:"Every time you reach to scroll, do one thing off your Dopamine Menu instead. Count how many.",w:"You're not removing the urge, you're redirecting it. Every swap is a rep that rewires the reward loop toward real things.",r:"How many swaps did you make today? Which one felt best?"},
    {e:"🏃",t:"Move your body",a:"20 minutes of movement — walk, gym, dance, anything that gets you breathing.",w:"Movement is the cleanest dopamine there is, plus endorphins. It proves to your brain that effort feels good.",r:"What did you do, and how did your head feel after?"},
    {e:"🤝",t:"One real connection",a:"Have one genuine, phone-down conversation. Call someone or meet up in person.",w:"Real connection is one of the strongest natural rewards we have — and the first thing screens quietly steal.",r:"Who did you connect with? What did it feel like to be fully present?"},
    {e:"🧭",t:"Design your normal",a:"Write the 3 rules you're keeping for good. Lock in the version of you you've felt this week.",w:"A reset only lasts if you decide what stays. Three simple rules beat a vague 'I'll do better' every time.",r:"What are your 3 rules — and who are you becoming by keeping them?"}
  ];
  var URGES=[{e:"🗣️",k:"Name it",v:"Say out loud: \"This is just a dopamine craving.\" Naming it shrinks it instantly."},
    {e:"🌬️",k:"Breathe x10",v:"Stand up, 10 slow breaths. The urge peaks and fades in under 2 minutes."},
    {e:"💧",k:"Cold water",v:"Drink a full glass of water or splash your face. Resets the impulse."},
    {e:"☀️",k:"60s outside",v:"Step outside for 60 seconds of daylight. Real light beats the screen pull."},
    {e:"⏳",k:"Do nothing",v:"5-minute timer, do literally nothing. Boredom is the reset, not the enemy."},
    {e:"✅",k:"Tiny task",v:"Make your bed, wash a cup. One small real action kills the itch."}];
  var MENU=[{e:"🚶",t:"10-min walk, no phone"},{e:"💪",t:"20 push-ups or stretch"},{e:"💬",t:"Message a friend something real"},
    {e:"📖",t:"Read 5 pages"},{e:"🛠️",t:"Make something with your hands"},{e:"🧹",t:"Tidy one small corner"},
    {e:"🌳",t:"Step outside, look up 1 min"},{e:"✍️",t:"Write one journal line"},{e:"☕",t:"Make a slow coffee/tea"},{e:"⭐",t:"Plan something to look forward to"}];
  var FACES=[{e:'😭',n:'Terrible',say:"Rough one. That's allowed. Do ONE tiny thing — a game or 3 breaths — and call today a win."},
    {e:'☹️',n:'Bad',say:"Heavy day. Don't push hard — just don't feed the scroll. Try the Breathing Bubble for 60s."},
    {e:'😐',n:'Okay',say:"Flat is normal mid-reset. This is the fog lifting. Knock out today's challenge — momentum beats mood."},
    {e:'🙂',n:'Good',say:"Love that. Ride it — do today's challenge now while you've got lift."},
    {e:'😀',n:'Amazing',say:"There it is. THIS is the reset working. Bank it — finish today and maybe a bonus game."}];
  var JOURNEYS=[
    {e:'😀',n:'Happy',g:GRADS[0],advice:"Don't just enjoy it — anchor it. Notice what got you here so you can do it again.",breath:"Box breathing: in 4, hold 4, out 4, hold 4.",quote:"\"The little things? The little moments? They aren't little.\" — Jon Kabat-Zinn",challenge:"Message someone and tell them why you appreciate them.",music:"Upbeat indie / feel-good playlist"},
    {e:'🚀',n:'Motivated',g:GRADS[4],advice:"Motivation is fuel, not a plan. Pour it into ONE action in the next 10 minutes.",breath:"Energising breath: 2 quick in through the nose, 1 long out. x10.",quote:"\"Discipline is choosing between what you want now and what you want most.\"",challenge:"Start the hardest thing on your list for just 5 minutes.",music:"Lo-fi focus / hype beats"},
    {e:'😰',n:'Anxious',g:GRADS[2],advice:"Anxiety lives in the future. Pull yourself back to right now — name 5 things you can see.",breath:"Long exhale: in 4, out 8. The long out switches off fight-or-flight.",quote:"\"You have survived 100% of your worst days. Breathe.\"",challenge:"Write the worry down, then one tiny step you can control.",music:"Calm ambient / piano"},
    {e:'😢',n:'Sad',g:GRADS[5],advice:"You don't have to fix it. Just don't numb it with a screen. Move your body gently.",breath:"Sigh it out: deep in, then a big audible sigh. x5.",quote:"\"Rock bottom became the solid foundation on which I rebuilt my life.\" — J.K. Rowling",challenge:"10-minute walk outside, even slow. Light helps more than you think.",music:"Warm acoustic / soft soul"},
    {e:'🤯',n:'Stressed',g:GRADS[1],advice:"Stress means too much at once. Brain-dump everything, then pick ONE.",breath:"Physiological sigh: 2 sniffs in, long out. x6.",quote:"\"You can do anything, but not everything.\"",challenge:"Close 5 browser tabs / clear one small space. Order calms the mind.",music:"Nature sounds / deep focus"}
  ];
  var QUOTES=[
    {t:"You don't have to be extreme, just consistent.",b:"—"},
    {t:"The pain of discipline weighs ounces. The pain of regret weighs tonnes.",b:"—"},
    {t:"Your brain isn't broken. It's just been overfed. Starve the noise.",b:"Dopamine Reset"},
    {t:"Boredom is the doorway to a calmer mind.",b:"—"},
    {t:"Every time you resist, you get stronger. Every time you scroll, it does.",b:"—"},
    {t:"You will never always be motivated. You must learn to be disciplined.",b:"—"},
    {t:"Small habits don't add up. They compound.",b:"James Clear"},
    {t:"The person you'll be in a year is built by what you do today.",b:"—"},
    {t:"Real life is slower than a feed. That's the point.",b:"Dopamine Reset"},
    {t:"Comparison is the thief of joy.",b:"Theodore Roosevelt"},
    {t:"Focus is a muscle. You're in the gym right now.",b:"—"},
    {t:"What you feed grows. Feed the real stuff.",b:"—"}];
  var LEVELS=[{x:0,n:'Asleep',b:'🌱'},{x:60,n:'Waking up',b:'☕'},{x:140,n:'Clearing',b:'⚡'},{x:240,n:'Locked in',b:'🔥'},{x:360,n:'Glowing',b:'🌟'},{x:500,n:'Golden Mind',b:'💎'}];
  var GAMES=[{id:'breathe',e:'🫧',t:'Breathing Bubble'},{id:'focus',e:'⏳',t:'Focus Timer'},{id:'resist',e:'🛡️',t:'Tap to Resist'},{id:'react',e:'⚡',t:'Reaction Test'}];
  var ACHV=[
    {id:'first',e:'👣',n:'First step',d:'Finish Day 1',test:function(){return state.done[0]}},
    {id:'checkin',e:'💗',n:'Tuned in',d:'Log your mood',test:function(){return ck()>0}},
    {id:'game1',e:'🎮',n:'First game',d:'Play any mind game',test:function(){return gp()>0}},
    {id:'crave',e:'💪',n:'Urge crusher',d:'Beat 3 cravings',test:function(){return state.crave>=3}},
    {id:'s3',e:'🔥',n:'On a roll',d:'3-day streak',test:function(){return streak()>=3}},
    {id:'why',e:'🧭',n:'Know your why',d:'Fill all 4 Why boxes',test:function(){return vf()>=4}},
    {id:'mind',e:'🧠',n:'Mind gym',d:'Play 3 games',test:function(){return gp()>=3}},
    {id:'journal',e:'📓',n:'Reflective',d:'Write a journal line',test:function(){return (state.journal||'').length>3}},
    {id:'xp250',e:'⭐',n:'Locked in',d:'Reach 250 XP',test:function(){return xp()>=250}},
    {id:'reset',e:'🏆',n:'Full reset',d:'Complete all 7 days',test:function(){return dc()>=7}}
  ];

  function dc(){var n=0;for(var i=0;i<7;i++)if(state.done[i])n++;return n}
  function cur(){for(var i=0;i<7;i++)if(!state.done[i])return i;return 6}
  function streak(){var s=0;for(var i=0;i<7;i++){if(state.done[i])s++;else break}return s}
  function pct(){return Math.round(dc()/7*100)}
  function ck(){return Object.keys(state.moods).length}
  function gp(){return Object.keys(state.games).length}
  function vf(){var n=0;for(var i=0;i<4;i++)if((state.vision[i]||'').length>1)n++;return n}
  function xp(){var x=dc()*30+state.crave*5+ck()*10+gp()*15+vf()*5+state.savedQ.length*2;if((state.journal||'').length>3)x+=10;return x}
  function lvl(){var x=xp(),L=0;for(var i=0;i<LEVELS.length;i++)if(x>=LEVELS[i].x)L=i;return L}
  function clamp(v){return v<0?0:v>100?100:Math.round(v)}
  function avgMood(){var v=[],k;for(k in state.moods)v.push(state.moods[k]);if(!v.length)return -1;var s=0;for(var i=0;i<v.length;i++)s+=v[i];return s/v.length}

  // confetti + toast
  var cf=$('#drCf'),toastEl=$('#drToast'),toastT;
  function confetti(){if(!cf)return;var c=['#ffc24b','#ff5c8a','#7c5cff','#5ad48a','#2bd3c6'],h='';for(var i=0;i<28;i++)h+='<span style="left:'+Math.random()*100+'%;background:'+c[i%5]+';animation-duration:'+(1.1+Math.random()*1.2)+'s;animation-delay:'+(Math.random()*.3)+'s"></span>';cf.innerHTML=h;setTimeout(function(){cf.innerHTML=''},2700)}
  function toast(msg){if(!toastEl)return;toastEl.innerHTML=msg;toastEl.classList.add('on');clearTimeout(toastT);toastT=setTimeout(function(){toastEl.classList.remove('on')},2600)}

  // modal
  function closeM(){clearGame();$('#drModal').classList.remove('on')}
  function openModal(){$('#drModal').classList.add('on')}
  function openDay(i){
    if(i>dc())return;var d=DAYS[i];
    $('#mTop').style.background=GRADS[i];$('#mEmoji').textContent=d.e;
    $('#mTag').textContent='Day '+(i+1)+' · your mission';$('#mTitle').textContent=d.t;
    $('#mBody').innerHTML='<p style="margin:0 0 4px;color:var(--ink)">'+d.a+'</p>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>🧠 Why this works</b><p>'+d.w+'</p></div>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>✍️ Reflect</b><p>'+d.r+'</p><textarea class="mnote" id="mNote" placeholder="Write a line for today…">'+(state.notes[i]||'')+'</textarea></div>';
    var done=state.done[i];
    $('#mAction').innerHTML='<div class="msec"><button class="btn btn--g" id="mDoneBtn" style="width:100%">'+(done?'Mark not done':'Complete Day '+(i+1)+' · +30 XP ✓')+'</button></div>';
    $('#mDoneBtn').onclick=function(){var n=$('#mNote');if(n)state.notes[i]=n.value;save();toggle(i);closeM()};
    var nt=$('#mNote');if(nt){var tm;nt.addEventListener('input',function(){clearTimeout(tm);tm=setTimeout(function(){state.notes[i]=nt.value;save()},500)})}
    openModal();
  }
  function openTile(o){$('#mTop').style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,var(--violet),var(--pink))';$('#mEmoji').textContent=o.e;$('#mTag').textContent=o.k?'Urge-surf':'Do it now';$('#mTitle').textContent=o.k||o.t;$('#mBody').innerHTML='<p style="margin:0;color:var(--soft)">'+(o.v||'Go do it now — that’s the whole point.')+'</p>';$('#mAction').innerHTML='';openModal()}
  function openJourney(j){
    $('#mTop').style.background=j.g;$('#mEmoji').textContent=j.e;$('#mTag').textContent='Feeling '+j.n;$('#mTitle').textContent='When you feel '+j.n.toLowerCase();
    $('#mBody').innerHTML='<div class="msec"><b>💡 Advice</b><p>'+j.advice+'</p></div>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>🫁 Breathe</b><p>'+j.breath+'</p></div>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>🎯 Try this</b><p>'+j.challenge+'</p></div>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>📜 Read this</b><p style="font-style:italic">'+j.quote+'</p></div>'+
      '<div class="msec"><b>🎧 Sounds for it</b><p>'+j.music+'</p></div>';
    $('#mAction').innerHTML='<div class="msec"><button class="btn btn--g" id="jrBreathe" style="width:100%">Do a 1-min breathing reset 🫧</button></div>';
    $('#jrBreathe').onclick=function(){openGame('breathe')};
    openModal();
  }

  // games
  var gTimers=[];
  function clearGame(){for(var i=0;i<gTimers.length;i++){clearTimeout(gTimers[i]);clearInterval(gTimers[i])}gTimers=[]}
  function gameDone(id,msg){if(!state.games[id]){state.games[id]=true;save();celebrate();toast('🎮 +15 XP · '+msg)}else{toast(msg)}render()}
  function openGame(id){
    clearGame();var g=null;for(var i=0;i<GAMES.length;i++)if(GAMES[i].id===id)g=GAMES[i];if(!g)return;
    $('#mTop').style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal),var(--blue))';$('#mEmoji').textContent=g.e;$('#mTag').textContent='Mind game';$('#mTitle').textContent=g.t;$('#mAction').innerHTML='';
    if(id==='breathe'){
      $('#mBody').innerHTML='<div class="play"><div class="bubble" id="bub">Breathe in</div></div><p style="text-align:center" id="bubMsg">Follow the bubble for 4 rounds.</p>';
      var bub=$('#bub'),ph=['Breathe in','Hold','Breathe out','Hold'],sz=['scale(1.25)','scale(1.25)','scale(.75)','scale(.75)'],n=0,rounds=0;
      function step(){bub.textContent=ph[n];bub.style.transform=sz[n];if(n===0)rounds++;n=(n+1)%4;if(rounds>4){bub.textContent='Done 🌿';bub.style.transform='scale(1)';$('#bubMsg').textContent='Nice. Notice how the urge faded.';gameDone('breathe','Calm restored')}else{gTimers.push(setTimeout(step,4000))}}
      step();
    } else if(id==='focus'){
      $('#mBody').innerHTML='<div class="play"><div class="rt" id="ft">Pick a length</div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center" id="ftBtns"><button class="btn btn--g btn--sm" data-m="5">5 min</button><button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" data-m="10">10 min</button><button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" data-m="25">25 min</button></div><p style="text-align:center;color:var(--faint);margin-top:10px">Put the phone down. Come back when it rings.</p>';
      $('#ftBtns').addEventListener('click',function(e){var b=e.target.closest('[data-m]');if(!b)return;var sec=+b.getAttribute('data-m')*60,left=sec;$('#ftBtns').style.display='none';
        function tick(){var m=Math.floor(left/60),s=left%60;$('#ft').textContent=(m<10?'0':'')+m+':'+(s<10?'0':'')+s;if(left<=0){$('#ft').textContent='✓ Done';gameDone('focus','Focus locked in');return}left--;gTimers.push(setTimeout(tick,1000))}
        tick();});
    } else if(id==='resist'){
      $('#mBody').innerHTML='<div class="play" id="rsArea"><div class="rt" id="rsTxt">Tap the distractions before they vanish!</div></div><p style="text-align:center" id="rsMsg">20 seconds. Resisted: <b id="rsN">0</b></p>';
      var area=$('#rsArea'),score=0,left=20,ds=['📱','🎮','📺','🍔','🔔'];
      $('#rsTxt').style.opacity=.6;
      function spawn(){if(left<=0)return;var s=document.createElement('div');s.className='distract';s.textContent=ds[Math.floor(Math.random()*ds.length)];s.style.left=(10+Math.random()*72)+'%';s.style.top=(18+Math.random()*60)+'%';area.appendChild(s);var rm=setTimeout(function(){if(s.parentNode)s.parentNode.removeChild(s)},1100);gTimers.push(rm);s.addEventListener('click',function(){score++;$('#rsN').textContent=score;if(s.parentNode)s.parentNode.removeChild(s)});gTimers.push(setTimeout(spawn,650+Math.random()*350))}
      function clock(){if(left<=0){$('#rsMsg').innerHTML='Time! You resisted <b>'+score+'</b>. 🛡️';gameDone('resist','You beat the pull');return}left--;gTimers.push(setTimeout(clock,1000))}
      spawn();clock();
    } else if(id==='react'){
      $('#mBody').innerHTML='<div class="play" id="rcArea" style="cursor:pointer"><div class="react" id="rc" style="background:#3a2330">Wait for green…</div></div><p style="text-align:center;color:var(--faint)">Tap as soon as it turns green.</p>';
      var rc=$('#rc'),area=$('#rcArea'),ready=false,t0=0,armed=false;
      gTimers.push(setTimeout(function(){rc.style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,#5ad48a,#2bd3c6)';rc.textContent='TAP NOW!';ready=true;t0=Date.now()},1500+Math.random()*2800));
      area.addEventListener('click',function(){if(armed)return;if(!ready){rc.textContent='Too early! 😅';armed=true;gTimers.push(setTimeout(function(){openGame('react')},900));return}armed=true;var ms=Date.now()-t0;rc.style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,#ffc24b,#ff8a3d)';rc.textContent=ms+' ms ⚡';if(!state.react||ms<state.react){state.react=ms;save()}gameDone('react','Sharp reflexes')});
    }
    openModal();
  }

  function toggle(i){if(!state.done[i]&&i>dc())return;var was=state.done[i];state.done[i]=!state.done[i];if(!state.done[i]){for(var j=i+1;j<7;j++)state.done[j]=false}save();if(!was)celebrate();render()}

  function thumb(i){var d=DAYS[i],done=state.done[i],locked=i>dc();
    return '<div class="thumb'+(done?' done':'')+(locked?' locked':'')+'" data-day="'+i+'"><div class="thumb__bg" style="background:'+GRADS[i]+'"></div><span class="thumb__emoji">'+d.e+'</span><span class="thumb__tag">DAY '+(i+1)+'</span><div class="thumb__cap"><b>'+d.t+'</b><span>'+(done?'Completed':locked?'Locked':'Tap to open')+'</span></div></div>'}

  function setRing(id,nid,v){var r=$(id);if(r)r.style.setProperty('--v',v);var n=$(nid);if(n)n.textContent=Math.round(v)}

  function celebrate(){ // check for newly unlocked achievements + level
    render(true);
  }

  var lastLvl=lvl();
  function render(burst){
    // header / level
    var L=lvl(),lv=LEVELS[L],x=xp();
    $('#pXp').textContent=x;$('#pStreak').textContent=streak();$('#pDay').textContent=Math.min(dc()+1,7);
    $('#lvBadge').textContent=lv.b;$('#lvName').textContent='Level '+(L+1);$('#lvTitle').textContent=lv.n;
    var nx=LEVELS[L+1],into=nx?((x-lv.x)/(nx.x-lv.x)*100):100;$('#lvBar').style.width=Math.min(100,into)+'%';
    if(burst){var b=$('#lvBadge');b.classList.add('pop');setTimeout(function(){b.classList.remove('pop')},280)}
    if(L>lastLvl){confetti();toast('🎉 Level up — '+lv.n+'!');lastLvl=L}

    // coach
    var h=new Date().getHours(),greet=h<12?'Good morning':h<18?'Good afternoon':'Good evening';
    $('#coHi').textContent=greet+' 👋';
    var c=cur();
    $('#coSub').textContent='Day '+(c+1)+' of 7 · '+pct()+'% through your reset';
    var am=avgMood();
    var say=dc()>=7?"You finished the whole reset. Genuinely — that's rare. Keep one habit alive.":
            streak()>=3?("🔥 "+streak()+" days straight. Your brain is already rewiring. Today: "+DAYS[c].t.toLowerCase()+"."):
            dc()===0?"Let's get your first win. Today takes 10 minutes: "+DAYS[c].t.toLowerCase()+".":
            ("You're "+pct()+"% in. Next up: "+DAYS[c].t.toLowerCase()+". Small step, big compounding.");
    $('#coSay').textContent=say;
    var q=QUOTES[(new Date().getDate())%QUOTES.length];$('#coQuote').textContent='“'+q.t+'”';

    // today stats
    $('#t1').textContent=dc();$('#t2').textContent=streak();$('#t3').textContent=pct()+'%';$('#t4').textContent=state.crave;

    // feeds
    var fh=DAYS.map(function(d,i){return thumb(i)}).join('');
    if($('#dayFeed'))$('#dayFeed').innerHTML=fh;if($('#trackFeed'))$('#trackFeed').innerHTML=fh;
    if($('#trackBar'))$('#trackBar').style.width=pct()+'%';
    if($('#trackMsg'))$('#trackMsg').textContent=streak()>=7?"🏆 Full 7-day reset complete. Huge.":streak()>0?("🔥 "+streak()+"-day streak — keep it alive."):"Tap your first day to start the streak.";

    // stats / dials
    var reset=pct(),mood=am<0?0:am/4*100;
    var focus=clamp(28+dc()*8+gp()*4+streak()*2);
    var energy=clamp(32+dc()*6+mood*.3);
    var sleep=clamp(38+dc()*5+(streak()*3));
    var brain=clamp((reset+focus+energy+sleep)/4);
    setRing('#ringReset','#ringResetN',reset);$('#ringResetN')&&($('#ringResetN').textContent=reset+'%');
    setRing('#ringFocus','#rF',focus);setRing('#ringEnergy','#rE',energy);setRing('#ringSleep','#rS',sleep);setRing('#ringBrain','#rB',brain);
    if($('#sXp'))$('#sXp').textContent=x;if($('#sStreak'))$('#sStreak').textContent=streak();
    if($('#sTime'))$('#sTime').textContent=(Math.round((dc()*0.8+state.crave*0.05)*10)/10)+'h';
    if($('#sGames'))$('#sGames').textContent=gp();

    // mood graph
    var mg=$('#mgraph');if(mg){var hh='';for(var d=0;d<7;d++){var mv=state.moods[d];var ht=mv==null?6:((mv+1)/5*100);hh+='<div class="col"><div class="bar2" style="height:'+ht+'%"></div><div class="dl">D'+(d+1)+'</div></div>'}mg.innerHTML=hh;
      $('#moodMsg').textContent=am<0?'Log your mood each day to see it climb.':(am>=3?'Trending up — the reset is working. 🎉':'Early days. Watch this climb as you go.');}

    // achievements
    var ag=$('#achvGrid');if(ag){var got=0,hh2='';for(var i=0;i<ACHV.length;i++){var ac=ACHV[i],ok=!!ac.test();if(ok)got++;hh2+='<div class="ach'+(ok?' got':'')+'"><div class="e">'+ac.e+'</div><b>'+ac.n+'</b><span>'+ac.d+'</span></div>'}ag.innerHTML=hh2;$('#achvCount').textContent=got;$('#achvTotal').textContent=ACHV.length;
      // celebrate newly earned
      for(var i=0;i<ACHV.length;i++){var ac=ACHV[i];if(ac.test()&&!state.achvSeen[ac.id]){state.achvSeen[ac.id]=true;save();confetti();toast('🏆 Achievement: '+ac.n);}}}
  }

  // build static lists
  $('#urgeTiles')&&($('#urgeTiles').innerHTML=URGES.map(function(u,i){return '<div class="tile" data-urge="'+i+'"><div class="tile__bg" style="background:'+GRADS[(i+1)%7]+'"></div><div class="tile__in"><span class="e">'+u.e+'</span><b>'+u.k+'</b></div></div>'}).join(''));
  $('#menuTiles')&&($('#menuTiles').innerHTML=MENU.map(function(m,i){return '<div class="tile" data-menu="'+i+'"><div class="tile__bg" style="background:'+GRADS[i%7]+'"></div><div class="tile__in"><span class="e">'+m.e+'</span><b>'+m.t+'</b></div></div>'}).join(''));
  $('#gameTiles')&&($('#gameTiles').innerHTML=GAMES.map(function(g,i){return '<div class="tile" data-game="'+g.id+'"><div class="tile__bg" style="background:'+GRADS[(i*2)%7]+'"></div><div class="tile__in"><span class="e">'+g.e+'</span><b>'+g.t+'</b></div></div>'}).join(''));
  $('#journeyGrid')&&($('#journeyGrid').innerHTML=JOURNEYS.map(function(j,i){return '<div class="moodc" data-journey="'+i+'"><div class="cbg" style="background:'+j.g+'"></div><span class="e">'+j.e+'</span><b>'+j.n+'</b></div>'}).join(''));
  // mood faces (today)
  var mb=$('#moodBtns');if(mb){FACES.forEach(function(f,i){var b=document.createElement('button');b.className='moodb';b.title=f.n;b.textContent=f.e;b.setAttribute('data-face',i);mb.appendChild(b)})}
  // vision
  var VIS=[{e:'💰',t:'Money & freedom',p:'What would real freedom let you do?'},{e:'💪',t:'Health & body',p:'How do you want to look and feel?'},{e:'❤️',t:'People',p:'Who do you want to be fully there for?'},{e:'🧭',t:'Who you are becoming',p:'A year from now, who are you proud to be?'}];
  var vr=$('#visionRows');
  if(vr){vr.innerHTML=VIS.map(function(v,i){return '<div class="card" style="margin:0"><label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px"><span style="font-size:1.5rem">'+v.e+'</span> '+v.t+'</label><textarea data-vis="'+i+'" style="min-height:64px" placeholder="'+v.p+'">'+(state.vision[i]||'')+'</textarea></div>'}).join('');
    var vt;vr.addEventListener('input',function(e){var t=e.target.closest('[data-vis]');if(t){state.vision[t.getAttribute('data-vis')]=t.value;clearTimeout(vt);vt=setTimeout(function(){save();render()},600)}})}

  // quotes panel
  function showQuote(){var q=QUOTES[state.qi%QUOTES.length];$('#qText').textContent='“'+q.t+'”';$('#qBy').textContent=q.b||'';renderSaved()}
  function renderSaved(){var box=$('#qSaved');if(!box)return;$('#qSavedN').textContent='('+state.savedQ.length+')';if(!state.savedQ.length){box.innerHTML='<p style="color:var(--faint)">Tap ❤️ Save to keep the ones that hit.</p>';return}box.innerHTML=state.savedQ.map(function(t){return '<div class="qmini">❤️ <span>'+t+'</span></div>'}).join('')}
  if($('#qNext')){
    showQuote();
    $('#qNext').addEventListener('click',function(){state.qi=(state.qi+1)%QUOTES.length;save();showQuote()});
    $('#qSave').addEventListener('click',function(){var q=QUOTES[state.qi%QUOTES.length];if(state.savedQ.indexOf(q.t)<0){state.savedQ.push(q.t);save();toast('❤️ Saved');render()}renderSaved()});
    $('#qShare').addEventListener('click',function(){var q=QUOTES[state.qi%QUOTES.length];if(navigator.share){navigator.share({text:'“'+q.t+'” — via Dopamine Reset'}).catch(function(){})}else{toast('Copy: “'+q.t+'”')}});
  }

  // global click routing
  document.addEventListener('click',function(e){
    var go=e.target.closest('[data-go]');if(go){var p=go.getAttribute('data-go');$$('.dr__nav').forEach(function(n){n.classList.toggle('on',n.getAttribute('data-go')===p)});$$('.panel').forEach(function(s){s.classList.toggle('on',s.getAttribute('data-p')===p)});cs();window.scrollTo(0,0);return}
    if(e.target.closest('[data-open-today]')){openDay(cur());return}
    var dd=e.target.closest('[data-day]');if(dd){openDay(parseInt(dd.getAttribute('data-day'),10));return}
    var du=e.target.closest('[data-urge]');if(du){openTile(URGES[+du.getAttribute('data-urge')]);return}
    var dm=e.target.closest('[data-menu]');if(dm){openTile(MENU[+dm.getAttribute('data-menu')]);return}
    var dg=e.target.closest('[data-game]');if(dg){openGame(dg.getAttribute('data-game'));return}
    var dj=e.target.closest('[data-journey]');if(dj){openJourney(JOURNEYS[+dj.getAttribute('data-journey')]);return}
    var df=e.target.closest('[data-face]');if(df){var fi=+df.getAttribute('data-face');state.moods[cur()]=fi;save();$$('.moodb').forEach(function(x){x.classList.toggle('on',x===df)});var rep=$('#moodReply');if(rep){rep.style.display='block';rep.innerHTML='<h3>'+FACES[fi].e+' '+FACES[fi].n+'</h3><p style="margin:0">'+FACES[fi].say+'</p>'}celebrate();return}
  });
  $('#mClose').addEventListener('click',closeM);$('#drModal').addEventListener('click',function(e){if(e.target===this)closeM()});
  $('#craveBtn').addEventListener('click',function(){state.crave++;save();celebrate();var b=this;b.textContent='Another one beaten 💪';toast('💪 +5 XP');setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='I beat a craving 💪'},1100);$('#craveCount').textContent=state.crave});
  $('#rollBtn').addEventListener('click',function(){openTile(MENU[Math.floor(Math.random()*MENU.length)])});
  var j=$('#journal');if(j){j.value=state.journal;function js(){state.journal=j.value;save();var s=$('#jSaved');s.classList.add('on');render();setTimeout(function(){s.classList.remove('on')},1300)}$('#jSave').addEventListener('click',js);var jt;j.addEventListener('input',function(){clearTimeout(jt);jt=setTimeout(js,800)})}
  function os(){$('#drSide').classList.add('open');$('#drScrim').classList.add('on')}function cs(){$('#drSide').classList.remove('open');$('#drScrim').classList.remove('on')}
  $('#drBurger').addEventListener('click',os);$('#drScrim').addEventListener('click',cs);
  $('#craveCount')&&($('#craveCount').textContent=state.crave);

  render();
}catch(err){
  try{
    var m=document.querySelector('.dr__main');
    if(m)m.insertAdjacentHTML('afterbegin','<div style="background:#15121d;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:14px;color:#f6f4ef"><b>Your reset is loaded.</b><p style="color:#b8b4ad;margin:6px 0 0">A small visual hiccup happened — tap a menu item on the left to jump in, or pull to refresh.</p></div>');
  }catch(e){}
}
})();
</script>
